    {
      "text": "The Mario's Early Years! series is a trilogy of point-and-click educational games released on MS-DOS and Super Nintendo Entertainment System developed and published by The Software Toolworks under license from Nintendo. The three games consist of Fun with Letters, Fun with Numbers and Preschool Fun.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "La serie Mario's Early Years! è una trilogia di videogiochi educativi punta e clicca pubblicati tra il 1993 e il 1994 per MS-DOS e Super Nintendo Entertainment System da Software Toolworks. La serie è costituita da Fun with Letters, Fun with Numbers e Preschool Fun.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『マリオの幼年期！』シリーズは、任天堂からライセンスを得て、The Software Toolworksによって開発・出版された、MS-DOSおよびスーパーファミコン（Super Nintendo Entertainment System）向けのポアイント・アンド・クリック式の教育ゲームの三部作です。この3部作は、『Fun with Letters』、『Fun with Numbers』、そして『Preschool Fun』で構成されています。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
